teststorydesc: Due to an error in the IIS software, the IIS is unable to recognize the HL7 version ID sent in MSH-12 even though it is valid. The acknowledgement message returned contains an error for an unsupported version ID.
preCondition: A VXU message is generated by the EHR.
evaluationCriteria: The error returned in the acknowledgement message is visible in the system responsible for the content of the administration message.
